1.title: Sweat, Hot Lakebottom Summer/The S'Mogre
1.plot: McGee becomes a human sweat hydrant after using zombie Sawyer's anti-sweat cream./McGee gets covered in delicious s'mores toppings, and is transformed into a s'mores monster. A S'Mogre.

2.title: Camp Lockdownbottom/All You Need Is Larva
2.plot: Rosebud turns camp Lakebottom into camp LOCKDOWN-bottom. Keeping the kids behind bars until they return her missing golden ladle!/Squirt develops a case of worms so bad, they try to EAT all of the bottomdwellers.

3.title: Meet the Gretch's Parents/Now with 100% More Portal
3.plot: Gretch's famous action-hero, movie-star parents visit Camp Lakebottom, and wind up getting a dramatic motivation they never dreamed of: TERRIFIED BY MONSTERS!/The kids discover an inter-dimensional portal that takes them to a similar Lakebottom, where their inter-dimensional alter-egos are all Zombies.

4.title: Lakebo_tron/Rise of the Dawn of the Beginning of the Planet of Armand
4.plot: Buttsquat and McGee get digitized into a classic 80's video game, and must battle the game's software guardian to make their way out again./The bottomdwellers travel through the inter-dimensional portal to an all-Sasquatch version of Camp Lakebottom, where King Armand makes them his slaves.

5.title: McGee's First Flush/House of Earwax
5.plot: The campers face the wrath of two mutated Ocean Apes, once the pets of McGee and Suzi, now seeking for revenge after being flushed years ago./Squirt's ear wax gains it's own consciousness, and hypnotizes Squirt into replacing his friends with sculpted ear wax replicas.

6.title: Butt-Squad/You Sank My Battle-Squirt!
6.plot: Buttsquat uses all the evil tricks at his disposal to brainwash the kids into becoming an elite Butt-Squad of Buttsquat warriors!/An alien ship invades Camp Lakebottom, eager to snatch away the ultimate power in the universe. Which happens to be...Squirt?

7.title: I, Rodent/Undies Cover of the Night
7.plot: Rosebud and the kids are drawn into a Squirrel-version of Lakebottom to answer for their crimes against all Squirrel-kind!/McGee's nightmare of being seen in only his undies becomes reality, and the other kids must travel into his dreams to set things right again.

8.title: Afterlife of the Party/F.L.O.P.P.Y. The Elephant
8.plot: The kids must halt all partying at once, lest they summon the Party Animal to Lakebottom. And when he parties down, he REALLY parties down!/The kids befriend a lost circus elephant, only to discover it's part of Doofus the Clown's over-complicated plan to take over Camp Lakebottom.

9.title: The Lakebottom House of Horrors! Mwa Ha Ha! Pt 1/The Lakebottom House of Horrors! Mwa Ha Ha! Pt 2
9.plot: The kids enter a Lakebottom House of Horrors. Only to discover that they will soon be the house's star attractions!/The kids fight their way through the terrifying Lakebottom House of Horrors, closing in on the inevitable face off...with the mysterious Gluteus Crouch.

10.title: Tur-keepin It Real/Little Saint Nicky
10.plot: The kids must find their way out of a Lakebottom dimension populated by giant Turkeysaurus Rexes...before they wind up as Harvest dinner./McGee is desperate to get Santa Claus OUT of Lakebottom, after he crash-lands in camp. If he realizes that McGee was the one who sent him that mean letter, it's goodbye presents...forever.

11.title: Nostril-Damus!/Working Over-Slime
11.plot: McGee's toxic-rain induced cold causes his snot to attain future-telling powers. But these powers actually make AWFUL things happen...including a monster-attack...on Squirt!/The kids discover that Slimey is secretly hanging out with the bottomlurkers, and travel to Bottom-lake to confront their pal. That's when Buttsquat shows up, eager to make Slimey...into a plate of Butt-sushi.

imdb.title: Camp Lakebottom
plot: McGee sets out for summer camp but ends up in the wrong bus, where he meets Squirt and Gretchen. The bus ended up at _Camp Lakebottom_ (qv), a forgotten, weird place has a lot of adventures in store for the 3 friends and their enemy Buttsquat
synopsis: Teletoon's brand new animated series Camp Lakebottom follows a group of kids as they set out for the best summer for their lives at the most dangerous (and exciting) summer camp you can imagine!The Camp Director is a monster, the lake is called Ickygloomy and the oatmeal has a life of its own, but that doesn't stop Camp Lakebottom from being the best camp ever! Especially if you have a taste for the unexpected... Camp Lakebottom follows the adventures of 12-year-old prankster McGee and his summer at the most dangerous and exciting summer camp in the world. The cabins are run down, the lake is toxic, the forest creatures are mutants and the counselors are a freak show, but McGee and his friends Gretchen and Squirt are having the time of their lives. The only thing they could do without is that snooty kid, Jordan Buttsquat, from the squeaky clean rival camp across the lake, Camp Sunny Smiles.
